          <p class="text-charcoal opacity-70 text-sm">
            Typically 10 years. During this period you can borrow from your line, repay it, and borrow again. You pay interest only on what you have drawn.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-warm-cream p-8 rounded-md text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-warm-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-xl mx-auto mb-4">2</div>
